and this happened,
Gatsby is üíØ
now I can have as many emojis I want üòÉ &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Now Lets Talk vs code.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;which I liked the most is &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;Emoji
perkovec.emoji&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;which help to insert the emoji from command palate üëè,&lt;/p&gt;
